document_data.mainbody:
el was a female vampire who hunted Shadow Thieves in Athkatla in the late 14 century DR.
In the , the criminal underbelly of Athkatla erupted in an all-out guild wars between the Shadow Thieves and a vampire coven under the leadership of Bodhi. Del was a loyal follower of the covens leader and hunted down Shadow Thieves for her mistress. Sansuki was among those unfortunate thieves whom Del tracked and chased down across Athkatlas Scepter District along with two other bloodsuckers. Sansukis life was forfeit as he had no chance to stand against the undead. Later, she would chase Abdel Adrian on orders from Bodhi to the isle of Brynnlaw, along with vaporizes Valen and Parisa.
